Class JIPipeAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.nodes.JIPipeGraphNode
      • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.nodes.JIPipeAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeValidatable, JIPipeParameterCollection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefineRectangularRoiAlgorithm, DefineTablesAlgorithm, ExportDataByParameter, ExtractParametersAlgorithm, FileDataSource, FileListDataSource, FolderDataSource, FolderListDataSource, FormGeneratorAlgorithm, GraphWrapperAlgorithm, ImageTypeConverter, IOInterfaceAlgorithm, IteratingFormProcessorAlgorithm, JIPipeParameterlessSimpleIteratingAlgorithm, JIPipeParameterSlotAlgorithm, MergeDataSlots, MergingFormProcessorAlgorithm, ModifyAndMergeTablesScript, OutputFolderDataSource, ParametersDataDefinition, ParametersDataTableDefinition, PathDataSource, PathListDataSource, SimpleIteratingFormProcessorAlgorithm, SplitByAnnotation, TablesFromScript

    public abstract class JIPipeAlgorithm
extends JIPipeGraphNode
    An JIPipeGraphNode that contains a non-empty workload. This class contains additional parameters to control the workload behavior. Please prefer to use this class or its derivatives if you write your algorithms.
